message: The South Carolina Attorney General's Office will relaunch the Coastal Region Human Trafficking Task Force to help combat the crime in Horry and Georgetown Counties.

data.description: MYRTLE BEACH, SC (WBTW) - The South Carolina Attorney General's Office will relaunch the Coastal Region Human Trafficking Task Force to help combat the crime in Horry and Georgetown Counties.
data.title: Human trafficking task force to relaunch in Horry and Georgetown Counties
